game.name: Mr Lupato and Eldorado Treasure
game.description:
Mr. Lupato heads on a trip through a platform that is full of multiple deadly obstacles. He is very excited to seek for the much-awaited Eldorado treasures. Would you like to help him to overcome the unwanted hurdles to make his journey memorable forever? Join Mr. Lupato And Eldorado Treasure and be prepared to help him to jump timely and collect all gems and keys that you see along the way! Multiple spikes and other obstacles are also waiting for you in this brand new adventure game.

Keys that you find will help to open the door shown at the end of each level. Your performance in this free HTML5 platform game will decide how many stars you will grab out of the three. Do not forget to collect all of the beautiful diamonds, find 4 secret levels and make your character jumps as many times as you can. Guide him to reach to the exit gate through all unique and fabulous levels in this exciting and funny platformer!

He is looking for his most precious hidden treasures and you are his only hope so complete tasks in each level and make him feel proud on you once again. Time his jump and challenge his jumping abilities to avoid falling off the cliffs in this dangerous jungle! Track how many jumps you have to manage by looking at the top left corner of the screen while the top right corner of the screen will show you the status of your present level! This platform adventure game easy controls and colorful graphics.
